## 7. Risk Management Policy

### Risk Domains
- Blockchain protocol risk
- Smart contract and SDK risk
- Data privacy and compliance risk
- Third-party and vendor risk

### Risk Treatment
- Mitigation through technical controls
- Transfer via contracts or insurance
- Acceptance with documented approval

### Review Cycle
- Quarterly reviews
- Additional review before major Solana upgrades or SDK releases

---

## 8. Backup & Data Retention Policy

### Data Types
- KYC identity artifacts
- Compliance and audit logs
- Operational metadata

### Retention Periods
- KYC records: 5â€“7 years (jurisdiction dependent)
- Audit logs: minimum 2 years
- Operational backups: 30 days

### Security Controls
- Encryption at rest and in transit
- Least-privilege access
- Secure deletion at end of retention period

